item.description: I am a third year Ph.D. student in Computing and Information Science at the Golisano College of Computing and Information Sciences, Rochester Institute of Technology (RIT) . I am a Graduate Research Assistant under the supervision of Prof. Anne Haake and Prof. Rui Li. My research interests lie at the intersection of machine learning and network science, with a current emphasis on graph representation learning, graph neural networks and their application to computational biology.
